ygData.msgSnippet: Out of curiosity, has anyone fought Trakanon?  I hadn t heard anything and wondered if Trakanon had even been located yet.  I always like to hear tales of mobs
ygData.messageBody:
Out of curiosity, has anyone fought Trakanon? I hadn't heard anything and
wondered if Trakanon had even been located yet. I always like to hear tales
of mobs it's highly unlikely I will ever see.

Also, I fear I may have zoned into Dalnir when I went LD last nite from what
I heard from a friend. Is it reasonably easy to get out of Dalnir once you
get in?

Kitasi the curious

Given the uber-ness of the uber-mobs: Trakanon, whoever awaits in Veeshan's,
etc. Even at level 60 we will all be needing some of this uber-armor and
some uber weps. Now if we had some uber-instruments to go with the armor...

Sylly
